social_posts.post_text:
Season 2 of @thesexlivesofcollegegirls is OUT on @hbomax and I choreographed a few dance scenes!!! 
I loved every moment of being on this set. Being behind the camera is just as fulfilling as in front of for me and I continue to stay grateful for any hat I get to wear in this industry. 🥲✨

Assistant choreography for Magic Mike scene: @anthonybartley 🙏🏾

Also my sis @kileighwilliams held it down on set for a Cupid shuffle moment!!

I couldn’t tag everyone because there are more than 20 BUT most importantly to the dancers I had the pleasure of getting to know and to dear friends I got to hire, thank you so much and beyond for being y’all!!! Until the next…♥️
3 MORE DAYS until Beauty and The Beast 30th Anniversary premieres on @abcnetwork, @disneyplus next day!!! I can’t wait for you all to see the magic that was made. Please be our guest and tune in! ✨🌹

Tears of gratitude when it comes to this gig! When theatre and television come together it’s one of my favorite worlds to be in. Every artist in this room moved me in some way every day, and working with these incredible choreographers and being part of this prodcution has me feeling so appreciative of why we do what we love for this industry but also…for ourselves. I can honestly say I’m heading into 2023 feeling fulfilled yet inspired ✨

The BIGGEST thank you to @rajkapoorproductions @ritamayebland @jamizzi @dennathomsen @chrislxd @makenzie_dustman @phillipchbeeb @hayley.erbert @derekhough @willbbell @jamiendonovan @zacbrazenas @hamishhamiltontv @camwhitelaw for having me!!! The team of dreams! 

Also @marinatoybina where does one even begin when it comes to wardrobe!? 😍

30th Celebration of this Disney classic on @Disneyplus and @hulu! 🌹

#beautyandthebeast #doneanddusted
Because this cast made my heart so full. ♥️
This is the only rainy day I ever want to have 💙

Can’t wait to perform this rendition of “Pal Joey” Nov 1st-5th @NYCityCenter! This cast and the creatives are absolutely phenomenal and I’m still in awe to be a part of it. Hope to see you there!!! ✨ #PalJoeyNYCC

PAL JOEY ✨

I have SO much love for everyone that was involved in this beautiful process. I’m thankful for the journey and thankful for the practice of being nothing but present in every moment throughout this opportunity. Missing everyone already…
until the next time! ♥️
